"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:16:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平價嘅都係500 樓下打到underarm,3000左右打到小腿<br />\n你下下要啲咁出名嘅公司實貴咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n彩光脫毛post 有絲脫左兩年都仲有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係盞搞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇咁平阿 500樓下我怕效果弱打十次都仲生緊<br />\n加加埋埋可能仲貴過啲效果好既打四次<br />\n<br />\n好似話激光先係真正做到減毛<br />\n彩光係唔知咩暫停生毛兩個月 所以平<br />\n不過家用應該彩光都okay? 最多我勤力打😂"},{"pid":"2f0853efa6ee34e60dbd70c1ebf63a4c31253234","tid":309390,"uid":72469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:17:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用緊呢部。。 都幾好，打兩三次就有出少咗<br />\n但頭兩個月要好乖 個個禮拜打</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你買嗰時幾錢？我去格下價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f0134faeefca4a7877e3e0e8e48ec228f8faf96","tid":309390,"uid":656,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:22:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平價嘅都係500 樓下打到underarm,3000左右打到小腿<br />\n你下下要啲咁出名嘅公司實貴咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n彩光脫毛post 有絲脫左兩年都仲有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係盞搞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇咁平阿 500樓下我怕效果弱打十次都仲生緊<br />\n加加埋埋可能仲貴過啲效果好既打四次<br />\n<br />\n好似話激光先係真正做到減毛<br />\n彩光係唔知咩暫停生毛兩個月 所以平<br />\n不過家用應該彩光都okay? 最多我勤力打😂</blockquote><br />\n貴同平係用同一部機（m記部機個冷凍技術特別小小但係都係同一款機），效果好唔好係睇佢開幾度唔係睇佢收你幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地咁貴係俾租俾佣啲員工咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係邊頂得順一個月幾十萬租<br />\n總之彩光就沒完沒了，啲毛係會幼會生得慢但永遠都係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有激光大部分人都要打5次～10次先完全無再生<br />\n唔好諗到激光咁快見效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申做呢行<br />\n<br />\n[DBP係黑店] 開返個脫毛討論區先 #5<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/273079?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/273079?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n過隔離睇下啦"},{"pid":"4d30623ad575ad3a8b4a14a855ccbdf1bfef4fd8","tid":309390,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:38:12.000Z","msg":"有冇人用過pearlwax"},{"pid":"c9666ec9622da666aabccd8fad5a9310e9a7c20e","tid":309390,"uid":65893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:48:17.000Z","msg":"tria用緊很ok"},{"pid":"dea68ef91bfd35a6dbb4d82a59e6ed598d5fee2d","tid":309390,"uid":7211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T15:06:56.000Z","msg":"買左蔣怡個部2年半，係幼左 但仲係有<br />\n你要有心機lor"},{"pid":"04e0dda3a35cb67d2fe9c94f057f7d5fc488a9e5","tid":309390,"uid":4240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:15:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用silk'n la<br />\n記得amazon 唔好香港買</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打係買佢邊部<br />\n我見佢有express 好似幾好"},{"pid":"0699fcb65a0c5b293f1c732bc5dcde64ea33ca48","tid":309390,"uid":29717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T17:59:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用緊呢部。。 都幾好，打兩三次就有出少咗<br />\n但頭兩個月要好乖 個個禮拜打</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你買嗰時幾錢？我去格下價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同你條link同一間。<br />\n你想平，佢有部黑色平少少 個樣差唔多<br />\n佢話功能上冇咩分別"},{"pid":"eab65375be8d62fc821899032f698b810c303ddb","tid":309390,"uid":50242,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T20:23:18.000Z","msg":"用左幾年philips<br />\n係生得慢左同幼左<br />\n不過要勤力 同唔洗旨意有斷尾既一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d193d9569bd4562c6cad1b040918bcd4b37ba4","tid":309390,"uid":7245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T23:46:07.000Z